{"tid":1222701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急 頭先（14/6）大概21:15 有冇人經過尖沙咀海旁？","createTime":"2019-06-14T13:41:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-14T14:23:49.000Z","uid":14362,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"469a1adf79e6d71d4b21817907026e160fbead51","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:41:45.000Z","msg":"頭先同女朋友經過尖沙咀 一開始佢見到先 之後佢同我講我即刻抬頭 見到一個接近透明 好似下圖嘅嘢飛過 但分辨唔到佢有幾高 好似幾低飛 <br />\n就咁睇比至少比飛機大兩倍 但感覺上飛機飛得比佢高 所以實際應該冇咁大<br />\n另外速度亦都比飛機快兩倍到 飛得好穩定 而且冇乜特別聲音 飛咗過去會展嗰頭<br />\n一定唔會係飛機 因為完全冇燈 只係有一個好模糊嘅輪廓<br />\n有冇人知道係咩？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuAwzoh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuAwzoh.png&h=f9d44948&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65abecb5544478e1eaaee53a0245e6cb614507fd","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"今晚能見度仲要唔係話太差"},{"pid":"0fcd79cb40d2dddf63c7cb90a655e861bc2d68b6","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:47:32.000Z","msg":"真係冇人見到？普通飛機會唔會熄晒所有燈？"},{"pid":"72b1480c9a7c40dff167be10a5f93e60d470c15d","tid":1222701,"uid":172454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:47:43.000Z","msg":"唔好戇鳩啦"},{"pid":"ae429486f5bc1de6ed7e4709bd9589452773e13a","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:52:47.000Z","msg":"完全冇人知？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />飛咗過海"},{"pid":"d78522674a26ed9f914f5d77d79f3002c2ce256f","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:53:48.000Z","msg":"冇目擊者？"},{"pid":"3810bc4196d25bcff705f2775127c7c85c919b08","tid":1222701,"uid":14362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T13:57:17.000Z","msg":"似梯形，唔係尖頭"},{"pid":"c8434446f7a1641679688c0c720852df0d4c1f46","tid":1222701,"uid":22873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"re